name: Hidden #01
description:
The horrors of my self are hidden between the faces of my past
while the darkness of the night paints an uncertain future... 
perhaps my own delirium.

Maybe I can sight the craziness 
in the shards of a broken mirror.	

Maybe I can hear
the scream of my pain 
that had vanished
choked by my throat
thrust backward into
the depths of my soul
